[div class=p 
	[b 
		"About the TRICKS:
	]b
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		[b 
			"Conversation skip:
		]b
		" Normally use game retry can skip this, but without the Check point this trick is useless! Freeze and unfreeze the Monkey is the best to use! The game will check for conversation at 2 times: the moment the bat appears and when it totally appears, so there are 2 ways to use this trick: Freeze and unfreeze 2 times or just Freeze and wait for the bat totally appear, then unfreeze!
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		[b 
			"Damage level:
		]b
		" Min -> Normal ATK -> Jumping ATK -> Gold Monkey ATK -> Gold Monkey Jumping ATK -> Power Rod -> Gold Monkey Power Rod -> Max.   Power Rod has no effect with bosses
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		[b 
			"Running:
		]b
		" Using the Power Rod is faster than normal run, but Monkey will stun for a while, so in general, normal run is faster. To skip the stun, there are 5 ways: enter door, start conversation, climbing, freeze the Monkey or jump to cloud
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"If the Monkey flies on the cloud, you can skip the animation of doing thing, for example, load the gun, pull the switch...
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		[b 
			"Jumping:
		]b
		" Jump and instantly attack, after the attack finished, jump again. This allows Monkey to "fly" in the air but the height 
		[del 
			"cannot rise
		]del
		" can rise but a little. Jump and freeze the Monkey then unfreeze, and jump again (you can do this to infinity after you get infinite power), with this trick the height can rise much so Monkey can jump to the very high. 
		$LF
	]li
]ul
